---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About"
	description="About Journal — a privacy-first PWA journal in the oriz family."
>
	<header class="container-prose page-head">
		<p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">Journal</a> / About</p>
		<h1>About Journal</h1>
	</header>

	<article class="container-prose prose">
		<p class="lede">
			Journal is a privacy-first PWA for personal journaling — ten journal
			types, offline-first, fully on the Firebase Spark plan.
		</p>

		<h2>What this site does</h2>
		<p>
			Capture today, revisit a year, notice who you're becoming. Journal
			supports daily writing, gratitude, learning, reading, travel, work,
			fitness, dream, research, and reflection journals — plus any custom type
			you need. Moods, tags, favorites, pinned entries, calendar, timeline,
			memories, stats, goals, templates. Markdown editor with live preview,
			autosave every 4.5 s, full export to JSON / Markdown / ZIP, and import
			back from any of those.
		</p>

		<h2>Privacy by default</h2>
		<p>
			Your entries live in Firestore under your own user ID. Nobody else can
			read them. Account deletion is a single button that wipes every
			Firestore document owned by your <code>uid</code>. No tracking across
			sessions, no selling of data, no required signup — try it as a guest
			first.
		</p>

		<h2>Part of oriz</h2>
		<p>
			Journal is one site in the <a href="https://oriz.in">oriz family</a> —
			a free collection of static sites covering books, cards, finance, dev
			tools, blog, and journaling. Single sign-in via
			<code>auth.oriz.in</code> works across every site.
		</p>

		<h2>Open source</h2>
		<p>
			Source code lives at
			<a href="https://github.com/chirag127/oriz-journal">github.com/chirag127/oriz-journal</a>.
			Issues and PRs welcome.
		</p>
	</article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.page-head {
		padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #d9d0bd);
	}
	.eyebrow {
		color: var(--color-ink-muted, #6b6256);
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}
	.eyebrow a { color: var(--color-ink-muted, #6b6256); text-decoration: none; }
	h1 {
		font-family: var(--font-display, "Fraunces", serif);
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.prose {
		padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
	}
	.prose .lede { font-size: 1.1875rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
	.prose h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-display, "Fraunces", serif);
		font-size: 1.375rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
	}
	.prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
	.prose a { color: var(--color-sienna, #b45309); }
	.prose code {
		background: var(--color-paper-soft, #f1ece2);
		padding: 0.125em 0.375em;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 0.875em;
	}
	.container-prose {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin-inline: auto;
		padding-inline: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 2rem);
	}
</style>
